{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"710","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"史上全球最熱5月 西伯利亞氣溫比歷史平均高10度","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/06/05&nbsp; 20:33</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%991.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 616px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>哥白尼氣候變化服務表示，今年<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月西伯利亞氣溫普遍「高度異常」。其中在鄂畢河和葉尼塞河部分沿岸地區，今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月氣溫比<span lang='EN-US'>1981</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>2010</span>年同月均溫快高出攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>度。（圖取自維基共享資源網頁，版權屬公有領域）</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社巴黎<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>日綜合外電報導）歐洲聯盟（<span lang='EN-US'>EU</span>）氣候監測機構「哥白尼氣候變化服務」今天說，今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月全球氣溫是紀錄有史以來最熱<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月。而永凍土主要分布地西伯利亞，今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月氣溫更比歷史平均高出攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>度。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>「哥白尼氣候變化服務」（<span lang='EN-US'>Copernicus Climate Change Service</span>，<span lang='EN-US'>C3S</span>）指出，今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月全球氣溫比<span lang='EN-US'>1981</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>2010</span>年同月均溫高出攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>0.68</span>度。其中阿拉斯加、歐洲、南北美洲的部分地區，及非洲、南極洲的大片地區，今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月氣溫都高於歷史均值。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>哥白尼氣候變化服務表示，今年<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月西伯利亞氣溫普遍「高度異常」。其中在鄂畢河（<span lang='EN-US'>Ob River</span>）和葉尼塞河（<span lang='EN-US'>Yenisei River</span>）部分沿岸地區，今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月氣溫比<span lang='EN-US'>1981</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>2010</span>年同月均溫快高出攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>度，這些地方今年也「傳出河冰比一般紀錄提早解凍」。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%992.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 347px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>哥白尼氣候變化服務表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月西伯利亞氣溫普遍「高度異常」，<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月氣溫甚至比<span lang='EN-US'>1981</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>2010</span>年同月均溫快高出攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>度。（圖取自<span lang='EN-US'>twitter.com/CopernicusECMWF</span>）</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據哥白尼氣候變化服務的紀錄，北極大部分區域今年<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月的氣溫也比歷史均溫高。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>哥白尼氣候變化服務表示：「今年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月為止，過去<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>個月（全球）平均氣溫接近比（工業革命前）水準高出攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>1.3</span>度。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年通過的巴黎氣候協定，近<span lang='EN-US'>200</span>個國家承諾將地表均溫較工業革命前水準升溫控制在攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>度以內，並在可能情況下降至攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>1.5</span>度以內。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>西伯利亞與阿拉斯加的部分地區出現熱浪，將使得一些去年因破紀錄高溫助長爆發大規模森林火災的區域格外警惕。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>哥白尼氣候變化服務警告，這些區域地面下悶燒的「殭屍」火苗，有可能再度燃起。（譯者：楊昭彥<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>核稿：張正芊）<span lang='EN-US'>1090605</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006050319.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-06-08","clk_count":"313"}},"__N_SSG":true}